The '''Prophet's Message''' was the gospel of the [[Jeedai heresy|''Jeedai'' heresy]] preached by [[Nom Anor|Yu'shaa the Prophet]]. The Message drew many [[Yuuzhan Vong]], especially in castes other than the [[Shamed Ones]], to the heresy.

